supabase/.temp
# Never ship a host-generated deno.lock into images. A newer host Deno writes
# lockfile v5, which edge-runtime v1.69.5's older Deno can't read — it crashes
# the worker at boot ("Unsupported lockfile version 5"). Deps resolve from
# deno.json (and functions are vendored into eszips), so the lock isn't needed.
supabase/functions/deno.lock
